%H A029399 <a href="/index/Rec#order_33">Index entries for linear recurrences with constant coefficients</a>, signature (0,0,0,0,1,0,1,0,1,0,0,0,0,-1,0,-1,-1,0,-1,0,0,0,0,1,0,1,0,1,0,0,0,0,-1).
%F A029399 G.f.: 1/((1-x^5)*(1-x^7)*(1-x^9)*(1-x^12)).
%F A029399 a(n) = a(n-5)+a(n-7)+a(n-9)-a(n-14)-a(n-16)-a(n-17)-a(n-19)+a(n-24)+a(n-26)+a(n-28)-a(n-33). - _Wesley Ivan Hurt_, May 20 2021
%F A029399 a(n) = floor((2*n^3+99*n^2+1344*n-11057)/45360 + ((2*n^2+1) mod 3)*n/108 + ((n+2) mod 3)/6 + ((4*n^3+3*n^2+3*n+1) mod 5)/5 + ((n^3+4*n^2+5) mod 7)/7 + (2*((n+7) mod 9) - ((n+6) mod 9) - ((n+8) mod 9))/27). - _Hoang Xuan Thanh_, Jul 20 2026
